Comment:      G.Amsel Nucl.Instrum.Methods 92 (1971) 481;
     Differential cross sections of the reactions used to  analyze 
16O, 18O at 165 deg (from ref[1-3]) and 14N at 150 deg (from  [4]) 
are presented in graphical form and discussed.
[1] G.Amsel and D.Samual, Anal.Chem. v.39 (1967) 1689.
[2] G.Amsel et al. Rev.Phys.Appl. v.3 (1968) 373.
[3] J.P.Nadai, Thesis(Orsay, 1967).
[4] G.Amsel and D.David, Rev.Phys.Appl. v.4 (1969) 383;
    Intern.Conf. MIS structures (Grenoble,June 1969) p.243.
The data are given in lab system.

